▪ Track record of successful and timely delivery of high quality performance, while demonstrating resilience under pressure and in adverse circumstances;
▪ Demonstrated ability to quickly identify value drivers for commercial success and effectively prioritize activities with greatest impact on business performance;
▪ Displayed ability to identify and make sound decisions about critical issues in a complex and uncertain environment, while considering the broader and long-term implications;
▪ Demonstrated ability to leverage quality-driven performance and effective communication skills (F2F and virtual) to build trust-based relationships and effectively collaborate with stakeholders from various backgrounds and seniority;
